   Bazooka awakens inside a dark stasis pod. The hatch opens and he crawls out into the world. He has the memories of the DNA he scaned, an Anklosaurus. He knows he must get to a base, because he is in unfimaliar territory. 
   "No command codes yet. I can't Transform." He mutters to himself. "No matter, i will have them soon enough." 
   Nothing stops him in his seemingly mad persuit. Even the land slide didn't slow him down, just hurt his skin.
   Eventually he reached a base. He marched in. It was the Predacon base.
